{"TopicId":178168,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Mk2 Cargo bay door glitch","CreatedByName":"soridia","CreatedById":107620,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-09T10:02:35Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"soridia","CreatedById":107620,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-09T10:02:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGame version :\u00A01.4.5.2243 (Steam, x64) (\u002B just \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Environmental Visual Enhancement (mod)\u0022\u003EEVE\u003C/abbr\u003E, Scatterer visual mod, ALL parts are stock)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStock Mk2\u00A0cargo bay has a door angle\u00A0glitch.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe open\u00A0angle of the long\u00A0one and short\u00A0one are different.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u002220180909171413_1.jpg\u0022 height=\u0022574\u0022 src=\u0022https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-UWEUTu3PfL0/W5TbEmFzlEI/AAAAAAAAABY/ikh3iIb8zyYUENh5WP7POPcg4Yg-wSeaACLcBGAs/s1600/20180909171413_1.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen fully opened, those\u00A0lined up well,\u00A0but..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002220180909171618_1.jpg\u0022 height=\u0022574\u0022 src=\u0022https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-b73_xqO5504/W5TbE7K1JJI/AAAAAAAAABc/EDWCc3Y0LxY_WvtJxOumC9Odv54dcb9wgCLcBGAs/s1600/20180909171618_1.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002220180909171622_1.jpg\u0022 height=\u0022574\u0022 src=\u0022https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-YkMOfoXK68A/W5TbErlq46I/AAAAAAAAABU/iyVrOuZx0Z0ArrQ4Kgo-xbvZdk0nI41nwCLcBGAs/s1600/20180909171622_1.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen it\u00A0is not\u00A0fully opened, CRG-08 and CRG-04 doors are dislocated\u00A0even if \u0027Deploy Limit\u0027 are same. (I set this 50 for example)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002220180909172018_1.jpg\u0022 height=\u0022574\u0022 src=\u0022https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-PwUjVgF0_FI/W5TbGpya-4I/AAAAAAAAABo/mg1D38rdkIcX4ayF8xP7kUtmvbxv7_J6ACLcBGAs/s1600/20180909172018_1.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd the dislocation is also different between left and\u00A0right. (the Deploy Limit are\u00A0same.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(lastly,\u00A0sorry for my \u0027dislocated\u0027 English ;D\u003Cspan\u003E)\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"4x4cheesecake","CreatedById":187982,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-09T15:07:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know something similar happens to the MK3 cargo bay but only in the editor (and modifying the deploy limit should fixed it in the editor as well, at least temporary).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSince you didn\u0027t ask a question: is this some kind of a bug report or do you want some help to fix it? If it is the latter one, I\u0027m not quiet sure if anyone beside SQUAD can fix it anyway...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}